name: "Elon Musk" circa 2012
description: He is one of the richest people in the World. Serial entrepreneur and founder of PayPal, SpaceX, Tesla, and Nueralink. In 2021, Musk revealed that he has Asperger Syndrome, an Autism Spectrum Disorder. His ideas and innovative thinking surrounding the future evolution of humankind have inspired many around the world.
